{"tid":2178012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以前好鍾意睇蔡瀾","createTime":"2020-08-28T06:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T09:35:53.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5cf73d8e35d607a7cd4b606652824cbeca3bcd","tid":2178012,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"小學個陣<br />\n見電視有條阿伯<br />\n食咩食到津津有味咁<br />\n幾搞笑<br />\n就睇佢d文<br />\n蘋果 圖書館<br />\n同埋佢寫過幾本書係for後生<br />\n咁多專欄作家<br />\n好似得佢一個唔悶<br />\n唔說教<br />\n唔屌9 d後生<br />\n只談風月<br />\n好8 90年代香港紙醉金迷<br />\n仲活係經濟泡沫<br />\n個種感覺<br />\n但而家睇真係好離地<br />\n尤其後生<br />\n以前真係會信<br />\n人大左就好似咁<br />\n日日美食搞笑9up去旅行<br />\n時間真係好快<br />\n到自己做左大人<br />\n細個以為大個左既自己做唔到<br />\n做左個同細個既自己遍遍相反既人"},{"pid":"38931c4f33f4560ad7161a86ac07ac7341a58d60","tid":2178012,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"好中2佢d武俠小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bf214994bf77d357b646b52967b21034bfdb51","tid":2178012,"uid":339397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38931c4f33f4560ad7161a86ac07ac7341a58d60","tid":2178012,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"好中2佢d武俠小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"696197b2eb1980a42d2d58f2de879e9fa29fdf03","tid":2178012,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59bf214994bf77d357b646b52967b21034bfdb51","tid":2178012,"uid":339397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38931c4f33f4560ad7161a86ac07ac7341a58d60","tid":2178012,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"好中2佢d武俠小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"唔記係神調定大唐小雙俠"},{"pid":"bfe